com.kuka.mastering.provider

Class MasteringProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.mastering.provider.MasteringProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMasteringProvider

    public class MasteringProvider
extends Object
implements IMasteringProvider
    Wraps the mastering functionality. Encapsulates the mastering algorithm, the position mastering (unmastering, checking whether axis is mastered etc.) and checks validity of the operations.
    This element is an undocumented internal feature. It is not intended to be used by applications as it might change or be removed in future versions.
